spec_data.Name: python-gearbox
spec_data.Description:
gearbox is a paster command replacement for TurboGears2. It has been
created during the process of providing Python3 support to the TurboGears2
web framework, while still being backward compatible with the existing
TurboGears projects.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 01:10:37 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Command line toolkit born as a PasteScript replacement for TurboGears2
